NK040(thi)051:1: // dbang bskur chos kyi sgo 'byed bzhugs so //
NK040(thi)051:2: dbang bskur chos kyi sgo 'byed pa la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)051:6: dang po sbyor ba'i chos la gnyis ste /
NK040(thi)051:7: sta gon dang mjug chog gnyis so //
NK040(thi)051:8: dang po sta gon la lnga ste /
NK040(thi)051:14: dang po dkyil 'khor sta gon ni /
NK040(thi)051:15: man+dala gru bzhi dri bzang gis byug la /
NK040(thi)051:16: chang dang bdud rtsi'i chag chag gdab la /
NK040(thi)051:19: chos 'byung gis phyi rol du mu khyud gru chad lha rnam dang ldan pa bri /
NK040(thi)051:20: de rgyab sgo bzhi sgo rgyan ldan pa bri /
NK040(thi)051:21: de rgyab rdo rje rwa ba me ris bskor /
NK040(thi)051:22: chos 'byung gis mtshams su g.yu drung 'khyil pa bri /
NK040(thi)051:23: tshon kha dog ni chos 'byung dmar po /
NK040(thi)051:28: lha rnam dang sgo bzhi phyogs mtshon no //
NK040(thi)051:29: sgo rgyan la sogs spyi mthun no //
NK040(thi)051:30: yang na dra phyi nang gtsang ma'i steng du /
NK040(thi)051:31: dri bzang gi chu gtor zhing /
NK040(thi)051:32: swa b+ha was stong par sbyangs /
NK040(thi)051:33: de'i steng du tshom bu bkod pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:39: ti ta badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK040(thi)051:40: zhes brjod pa dang sprad cing /
NK040(thi)051:41: dbus su tshom bu bkod la /
NK040(thi)051:43: de bzhin phyogs bzhir tshom bu bzhi /
NK040(thi)051:44: sngags dang bcas pa bkod la /
NK040(thi)051:47: gnyis pa mchod pa sta gon ni /
NK040(thi)051:49: tshom bu'i tha mar mchod pa rnams lnga dpung che ba bskor /
NK040(thi)051:50: dkyil 'khor shar du tshangs thig gis steng du /
NK040(thi)051:52: rnam rgyal bum pa kha rgyan tshang ba bshams la /
NK040(thi)051:54: sbrang chang la sin+d+hu ra bdal /
NK040(thi)051:55: de'i khar me long gis steng du dar gyis bkab nas bum pa'i khar bshams /
NK040(thi)051:56: las bum byang shar mtshams su bsham /
NK040(thi)051:57: de nas ma cig gis gtor ma ni /
NK040(thi)051:58: gdan zla gam gyi steng du gtor ma zlum po che ba gcig la /
NK040(thi)051:59: bshos bran zlum po bzhi bskor /
NK040(thi)051:60: yang na yum chen gyi gtor ma ni /
NK040(thi)051:61: gtor ma zlum po che ba gcig la /
NK040(thi)051:64: yum chen la sogs grub thob gcod brgyud kyis tsaka lis brgyan nas nub tu bshams /
NK040(thi)051:65: shar du bla ma'i gtor ma bshams /
NK040(thi)051:66: yang na dbang gtor dang gnyis ka gcig la bsdu bas chog gsungs /
NK040(thi)051:67: zur bzhir gtor chen bzhi g.yon bskor du bshams /
NK040(thi)051:72: yang na gral thabs su bshams /
NK040(thi)051:73: sngon 'gro'i gtor ma bshos bu snying 'dra ba zur zlum cig gang bder bshams /
NK040(thi)051:74: yang na bla ma dang zhi ba dbyer med gcig /
NK040(thi)051:75: yi dam khro bo la gcig /
NK040(thi)051:77: mkha' 'gro spyi gtor gcig dang lnga /
NK040(thi)051:78: dbang gtor dang sngon 'gro gtor ma gong dang mthun /
NK040(thi)051:79: gang ltar yin kyang tshogs gtor rin chen dpung pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:80: gdan zlum po'i steng du nor bu bzhi tshom gcig bzhag /
NK040(thi)051:81: de la ru lu mang pos bskor ba /
NK040(thi)051:82: spung che ba gcig la sha chang bza' bca' bcas shar lhor bshams /
NK040(thi)051:83: nang mchod sman chang mdun du bsham /
NK040(thi)051:84: des mchod pa sta gon song /
NK040(thi)051:85: gzhan yang grib gtor rdzas bzhi 'tshag bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:86: gsum pa lha sta gon ni /
NK040(thi)051:87: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i mngon rtogs tshogs las kyi nang na yod pa ltar byed cing /
NK040(thi)051:88: zhor la bdag 'jug len pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:89: gzhan la dbang ci ltar bkur ba bzhin du /
NK040(thi)051:90: rang gi yang de ltar len pa yin no //
NK040(thi)051:92: bzhi pa bum pa sta gon ni /
NK040(thi)051:93: rnam rgyal dang las bum gnyis /
NK040(thi)051:94: mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i mngon rtogs tshogs las kyi nang
NK040(thi)051:95: na yod pa ltar bum pa gnyis bskyed par bya'o
NK040(thi)051:96: // des bum pa sta gon song /
NK040(thi)051:97: lnga pa slob ma sta gon la drug ste /
NK040(thi)051:98: dang po grib chog byed pa /
NK040(thi)051:99: gnyis pa las rgyu 'bras dang lo rgyus bshad pa /
NK040(thi)051:100: gsum pa man+dala phul shing skyabs 'gro sems bskyed kyi sdom pa 'bog pa /
NK040(thi)051:101: bzhi pa gsol ba gdab cing len mo byin pa /
NK040(thi)051:102: lnga pa rang gzhung gi skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed kyi sdom pa zhu ba dang /
NK040(thi)051:103: drug pa rdzas bzhi gtad pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:105: dbang bskur spyi dang mthun no //
NK040(thi)051:106: gnyis pa las rgyu 'bras dang lo rgyus rgyas pa gzhan du shes so //
NK040(thi)051:108: dus da res thub pa'i bstan pa rin po che 'di la rten mi lus gtsang ma thob /
NK040(thi)051:110: rgyud la dad pa rten po skyes /
NK040(thi)051:111: yul bla ma mtshan ldan dang mjal /
NK040(thi)051:112: chos pha rol phyin ma bdud kyi gcod yul 'di nyid nyams su blang rgyu yod pa 'di /
NK040(thi)051:113: 'o skol rnams kyis bsod nams bsags pa yin /
NK040(thi)051:114: de lta bu'i chos nyams su len par byed pa la /
NK040(thi)051:115: phyi ltar na pha rol tu phyin pa'i dgongs pa yin /
NK040(thi)051:116: nang ltar na gsang sngags kyi lta ba yin /
NK040(thi)051:117: gsang ba ltar na rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud nyams su len pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:118: 'dir ngo sprod 'bog pa'i sngon du rgyud smin par byed pa'i thabs zab mo /
NK040(thi)051:119: snod du rung bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK040(thi)051:121: dbang thob pa byed pa yin /
NK040(thi)051:122: gsum pa man+dala 'bul zhing thun mong gi skyabs 'gro
NK040(thi)051:123: sems bskyed kyi sdom pa 'bog pa spyi dang mthun
NK040(thi)051:125: bzhi pa gsol ba gdab pa cing lan mo sbyin pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:126: slob mas man+dala 'bul zhing de nas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:127: dga' chen khyod bdag ston pa ste //
NK040(thi)051:128: slob dpon khyod ni dgongs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:129: byang chub chen po'i tshul bstan pa //
NK040(thi)051:130: mgon po chen po bdag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)051:131: dam tshig de nyid bdag la stsol //
NK040(thi)051:132: byang chub sems kyang bdag la stsol //
NK040(thi)051:133: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun ste //
NK040(thi)051:134: skyabs gsum dag kyang bdag la rtsol //
NK040(thi)051:135: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK040(thi)051:136: mgon po'i bdag nyid bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:137: ces lan gsum gsol ba gdab /
NK040(thi)051:139: bu khyod su yin ci la dga' /
NK040(thi)051:141: skal bzang bdag la bde chen 'tshal /
NK040(thi)051:145: sangs rgyas mchog gis dam tshig go //
NK040(thi)051:147: lnga pa rang gzhung gi skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sdom pa zhu ba las /
NK040(thi)051:148: dang po skyabs su 'gro ba 'di'i rjes bzlos mdzod /
NK040(thi)051:149: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun tshogs bcas la //
NK040(thi)051:150: byang chub ma thob par du bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK040(thi)051:151: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las bsgral bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK040(thi)051:152: dkon mchog gsum gyi rjes su bzung du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:153: lan gnyis pa dang gsum pa'i rjes zlos brjod /
NK040(thi)051:156: rigs kyi bu khyed rang rnams so sor thar pa'i
NK040(thi)051:157: rigs bdun las gang yang rung ba'i sdom pa dang
NK040(thi)051:158: / byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa dang /
NK040(thi)051:159: rig pa sngags kyis dam tshig las /
NK040(thi)051:166: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:167: 'khor ba sdug bsngal bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK040(thi)051:168: mi dge spang ba'i tshul khrims dang //
NK040(thi)051:169: dge ba'i chos bsdud tshul khrims dang //
NK040(thi)051:170: dge ba'i chos rnams sdud pa dang //
NK040(thi)051:171: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
NK040(thi)051:172: bdag gis brtan por bzung bar bgyis //
NK040(thi)051:173: deng nas bzung ste mi spang bzhin //
NK040(thi)051:174: gus pa'i tshul gyis bslab par bagyi'o //
NK040(thi)051:176: lnga pa rang gi skyabs 'gro sems bskyed song nas /
NK040(thi)051:177: drug pa rdzas bzhi gtad pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:178: de nas rdzas bzhi'i man+dala ni /
NK040(thi)051:179: dkyil 'khor lho phyogs su tshom bu lnga bkod la /
NK040(thi)051:180: dang po bzang shing 'bras bu dang /
NK040(thi)051:181: me tog bdud rtsi can sor bcu gnyis pa /
NK040(thi)051:182: rtse la dri bzang gis byug pa thog la /
NK040(thi)051:183: dang po tshem shing gleng gzhi brjod pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:184: lho phyogs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa bzhad pa lam la gnas nas /
NK040(thi)051:185: byang chub sems dpa'i mdzad pa mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK040(thi)051:186: mngon par shes pa sems can la gzigs nas /
NK040(thi)051:187: sems can gyi skye ba snga ma la /
NK040(thi)051:191: slob dpon du gyur pa las kyi kha lo bsgyur nas /
NK040(thi)051:192: 'dir sems can du skyes pa'i sha zos nas /
NK040(thi)051:193: de'i rnam par smin pa de ni shin tu lci bas /
NK040(thi)051:194: de dag par bya ba dang /
NK040(thi)051:195: ngag la byung ba'i nyes pa thams cad dag par bya ba'i phyir /
NK040(thi)051:196: nga'i ming dang sngags kyis so shing la btab nas /
NK040(thi)051:197: yi ge brgya pa brjod cing so shing gis so'i rtsa ba brus nas /
NK040(thi)051:201: bzhad pa rdo rje dgyes pa'i /
NK040(thi)051:202: tshem shing dag gis mnos nas ni //
NK040(thi)051:204: phyin ci log bzhis dbang bsgyur bas //
NK040(thi)051:205: dge bshes pha ma gnyen 'dun gyis //
NK040(thi)051:206: las kyi 'khor ba'i sha zos pa //
NK040(thi)051:207: tshim shing dam tshig mnos pa 'di //
NK040(thi)051:208: skad cig yud la byang bar shog /
NK040(thi)051:209: badz+ra ha sa tram sarba pa pam b+hi shwa d+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)051:211: yig brgya brjod la so brus /
NK040(thi)051:212: tshe rab snga ma la pha ma gnyen bshes mkhan
NK040(thi)051:213: slob du gyur pa thams cad 'dir las kyi kha
NK040(thi)051:214: lo bsgyur bas / dud 'gror skyes pa'i sha zos
NK040(thi)051:215: pa'i rnam par smin pa dang khyad par du ngag
NK040(thi)051:216: las byung ba'i sdig pa dag par bsam la tshom
NK040(thi)051:218: ltas ni phyogs bzhin las bzhi /
NK040(thi)051:219: mtshams bzhi la phrin las bzhi /
NK040(thi)051:221: mthur du bstan na sa 'og gi dngos grub thob pa'i ltas te /
NK040(thi)051:223: lho phyogs su bstan na gshin rje'i bar chad 'ong
NK040(thi)051:224: dog yod pas dkyil 'khor la gtor ma re 'bul
NK040(thi)051:226: de nas dri bzang gis chus swa b+ha was dag
NK040(thi)051:227: byed kyis chu nus pa can du byin gyis rlab
NK040(thi)051:228: la / dri chab kyi gling bzhi ni /
NK040(thi)051:229: 'di yang nub phyogs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje gnon pa zhes bya ba /
NK040(thi)051:230: lam la gnas nas byang chub sems dpa'i mdzad pa mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK040(thi)051:231: mngon par shes pas sems can la gzigs nas /
NK040(thi)051:232: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad lus ngag yid gsum bag chags bcas la thugs rje skyes nas /
NK040(thi)051:233: dri chab la nga yi ming dang sngags btab la /
NK040(thi)051:235: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bag chags dag par 'gyur ro //
NK040(thi)051:236: zhes lung bstan pas de'i rjes 'jug pa yin /
NK040(thi)051:237: rdo rje rnon po thog med kyis /
NK040(thi)051:238: dag byed dam tshig mnos nas ni /
NK040(thi)051:239: lus ngag yid las byung ba yis //
NK040(thi)051:240: bag chags ma lus dag par shog /
NK040(thi)051:241: badz+ra tig sna h+r+ai b+hi shwa d+ha ya pa pam tsa pa sho d+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK040(thi)051:245: lus ngag yid gsum gyis bag chags thams cad dag par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:247: de nas srung skud dmar po lus ngag yid gsum
NK040(thi)051:248: gyi rtags sum bsgril gnyis steb la gtso bo'i sngags
NK040(thi)051:250: brjod cing mdud pa gsum mam bdun mdud cing /
NK040(thi)051:251: rdo rje lug brgyud du brlab pa thog ste /
NK040(thi)051:252: bsrung skud kyis gling bzhi ni /
NK040(thi)051:253: byang phyogs kyis de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje bsrung ba lam la gnas nas /
NK040(thi)051:254: byang chub sems dpa'i mdzad pa mdzad pa'i dus su
NK040(thi)051:255: mngon par shes pa'i sems can la lam gyis bar
NK040(thi)051:257: de la thugs rje skyes nas rgyu rung ba'i bsrung skud la /
NK040(thi)051:258: nga'i ming dang sngags kyis btab nas /
NK040(thi)051:260: bar chad las grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK040(thi)051:263: bsrung ba rdo rje go cha yi //
NK040(thi)051:264: bsrung skud dam tshig mnos nas ni //
NK040(thi)051:265: bdun nam nyi shu rtsa gcig gis /
NK040(thi)051:266: bar du sngags ste mdud bor nas //
NK040(thi)051:267: 'chi bdag bdud las rgyal bar 'gyur ro //
NK040(thi)051:269: badz+ra yak+sha h'u gis pho'i dpung pa g.yon /
NK040(thi)051:270: bud med kyi g.yas la btag ste /
NK040(thi)051:271: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyis go khrab dang ldan par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:274: dbang dngos grub du gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:275: tshe dbang phun tshogs pa'i skal par ldan par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:276: ces de nas ku sha gzhan gyis long la spyad pa che chung gnyis thog la /
NK040(thi)051:277: ku sha'i gling bzhi brjod pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:278: 'di yang shar phyogs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa rdo
NK040(thi)051:279: rje legs pa lam la gnas nas byang chub sems
NK040(thi)051:280: dpa'i mdzad pa mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK040(thi)051:281: mngon par shes pas sems can rnams la gzigs nas /
NK040(thi)051:282: sems can thams cad ma rig pa'i gtib 'og la /
NK040(thi)051:283: nga'i ming dang sngags kyis btab nas /
NK040(thi)051:284: sngas dang stan du byas nas rmi lam rno ba
NK040(thi)051:285: dang legs nyes dge sdig rnams shes par 'gyur ro
NK040(thi)051:287: de dang rjes mthun pa yin /
NK040(thi)051:288: rdo rje legs pa dgyes pa che //
NK040(thi)051:289: rab dgyes rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog /
NK040(thi)051:290: ku sha 'di ni khyod kyi long //
NK040(thi)051:291: khyod kyis nyal ba'i sngas stan gyis /
NK040(thi)051:292: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams kun /
NK040(thi)051:293: rmi lam du ni ci rmis pa /
NK040(thi)051:294: sang ni bdag la snyad par byos /
NK040(thi)051:300: seng+ge'i nyal stabs kyis bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyis phyogs su mgo ston la nyol dang /
NK040(thi)051:301: sang nang par dkyil 'khor chen po mthong bar 'gyur gyis /
NK040(thi)051:302: nang par rmi lam bzang ngan brtag la bshad pa gyis /
NK040(thi)051:303: bzang na brod pa bskyed dang /
NK040(thi)051:304: ngan na zhi ba'i sbyin sreg byed /
NK040(thi)051:305: de yan chad kyis sta gon song /
NK040(thi)051:306: spyi don gsum pa 'jug chog la bcu gcig ste /
NK040(thi)051:307: dang po gdong g.yog bcing ba /
NK040(thi)051:309: gsum pa gsol ba gdab pa /
NK040(thi)051:310: bzhi pa ye shes dbab pa /
NK040(thi)051:311: lnga pa me tog phul ba /
NK040(thi)051:312: drug pa sngags phreng du byin gyis rlabs nas slob ma la gtad pa /
NK040(thi)051:313: bdun pa spyan dar dbye ba /
NK040(thi)051:315: dgu pa dam chu blud pa /
NK040(thi)051:316: bcu pa bla ma'i bka' la nyan pa /
NK040(thi)051:317: bcu gcig pa dbang thob ma thob kyi skyon yon no //
NK040(thi)051:319: dar dmar po la rdo rje dkar po mig mang ris su bris pa res /
NK040(thi)051:320: gdong g.yog bcing pa'i mos pa gyis //
NK040(thi)051:321: ces brjod la dar dmar po'i gdong g.yog bcing ba'o //
NK040(thi)051:322: gnyis pa me tog gi phreng ba 'dzin la /
NK040(thi)051:323: u dum wa ri'i ma d+ha la //
NK040(thi)051:324: yung du dang ni ma ki ta //
NK040(thi)051:325: ka ni ka yi phreng ba 'di //
NK040(thi)051:326: legs par long la bus zung zhig /
NK040(thi)051:328: gsum pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:329: slob mas gsol ba gdab pa /
NK040(thi)051:330: ye shes dbab pa'i don du gsol ba gdab /
NK040(thi)051:331: snyam pa'i mos pa gyis la nga'i rjes zlos mdzod //
NK040(thi)051:332: 'gro ba'i bla ma ston pa po //
NK040(thi)051:333: sdug bsngal rgya mtsho bying ba las //
NK040(thi)051:334: mgon po khyod ni dpal du byon //
NK040(thi)051:335: deng 'dir bka' drin gnang du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:337: bzhi pa ye shes dbab pa la /
NK040(thi)051:339: 'o na thugs la ci lta ba bzhin du bzhag par zhu /
NK040(thi)051:340: slob bu rjes su 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK040(thi)051:341: bdud kyi gcod yul ngo sprod 'debs pa'i sngon du rgyu'i snod du rung ba'i phyir /
NK040(thi)051:342: dbang bskur ba'i thog mar ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:344: steng gi nam mkha' la ma cig lab kyi sgron
NK040(thi)051:345: ma brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang tha dad med
NK040(thi)051:346: par / sku gcer bu rus pa'i rgyan drug gis brgyan pa /
NK040(thi)051:347: thod skam lnga'i dbu rgyan dang /
NK040(thi)051:348: thod rlon gyis do shal byas pa /
NK040(thi)051:349: g.yas pas gser gyi d+aa ma ru stong gsum khyab par dkrol nas /
NK040(thi)051:350: g.yon pas dngul dkar gyi dril bu dkrol ba /
NK040(thi)051:351: mchan khung du kha tram ga bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)051:352: zhabs g.yon brkyang pas ro yi snying gnon pa /
NK040(thi)051:353: g.yas bskum pa rting pa'i bla la gtad pa /
NK040(thi)051:354: khams gsum zil gyis gnon nus pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK040(thi)051:355: 'khor du mkha' 'gro dpag tu med pas bskor ba /
NK040(thi)051:356: la las rdo rje'i glu len /
NK040(thi)051:357: la las rdo rje'i gar byed /
NK040(thi)051:358: la las rdo rje'i bro 'khrab pa'i dbus nas ma
NK040(thi)051:359: cig spyan gsum steng gis nam mkha' la gzigs pa
NK040(thi)051:360: / gar thab ling ling byed cing bro 'khrab pa'i lugs bzhin bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:361: mos gus tong tong byed la /
NK040(thi)051:362: de rnams kyi sku gsung thugs la +aahmh'u gsum byung
NK040(thi)051:363: nas khyed rnams kyi lus ngag yid gsum la sib
NK040(thi)051:364: sib thib par bsgom mdzod la /
NK040(thi)051:365: d+aa ru dang dril bu 'khrol la spos bsregs brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs byed tshar nas /
NK040(thi)051:366: spyi bo nas de rnams mar byon nas slob ma
NK040(thi)051:367: rnams kyi spyi bor thim pas slob ma'i lus ngag
NK040(thi)051:368: yid gsum la zag med kyi bde bas ltem ltem
NK040(thi)051:370: rdzas rgod gu gul dud pas bdug go //
NK040(thi)051:371: 'o de ltar byas pas sku pheb na gar byed pa 'khrab cing phyag rgya bsgyur ba'o //
NK040(thi)051:372: gsung pheb na sngags bzla ba'o //
NK040(thi)051:373: rgya gar skad dang ha ha hi hi'i sgra sgrog tu 'ong /
NK040(thi)051:374: thugs pheb na gsal stong 'dzin med kyis nyams su len pa 'char /
NK040(thi)051:376: nyams dga' ya le bar 'ong ngo //
NK040(thi)051:377: lnga pa me tog 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:378: sngon gyi yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa de la me tog phreng ba phog par gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:379: snyam pa'i mos pa gyis la nga'i rjes zlos mdzad /
NK040(thi)051:380: sangs rgyas dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK040(thi)051:381: bdag la thugs rje brtser dgongs nas //
NK040(thi)051:382: 'gro la phan pa'i gtso chen gyis //
NK040(thi)051:383: sman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:384: pra ti dza badz+ra sa ma ya ho /
NK040(thi)051:385: brjod la me tog dkyil 'khor la gtor ro //
NK040(thi)051:386: drug pa sngags phreng gtad pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:387: lha tshogs kyi sngags phreng du byin gyis brlab nas /
NK040(thi)051:388: slob ma rang la gnang bar bsam /
NK040(thi)051:389: me tog rin chen la sogs te //
NK040(thi)051:390: gang la phogs par rigs kyi lha //
NK040(thi)051:391: gtso ba'i rigs de 'grub nas ni //
NK040(thi)051:392: dngos grub byung ste the tshom med //
NK040(thi)051:394: bdun pa spyan dar dbye ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:395: ma rigs pa'i ling tog dang spyan dar /
NK040(thi)051:396: lhan cig tu bsal snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK040(thi)051:397: rdo rje mkha' 'gro deng khyod kyis //
NK040(thi)051:398: mig 'byed pa ni brtson par mdzod //
NK040(thi)051:399: phye bas thams cad mthong bar 'gyur //
NK040(thi)051:400: rdo rje'i mig ni bla na med //
NK040(thi)051:401: tsak+shu pra we sha ya h'uh spyan dar blang la /
NK040(thi)051:402: mig dang mi shes pa'i rab rib bsal bar bsam /
NK040(thi)051:403: brgyad pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:404: da khyed rang rnams sngon ma mthong ba'i dkyil 'khor bzang mthong snyams pa'i mos pa gyis /
NK040(thi)051:405: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog tu //
NK040(thi)051:407: da ni dad pa rab tu skye //
NK040(thi)051:408: khyed ni sangs rgyas dngos grub thob //
NK040(thi)051:409: dkyil 'khor kha dog ci 'dra dri don bshad do //
NK040(thi)051:410: dgu pa dam chu blud pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:411: gcod kyi gzhung du bshad pa bzhin du /
NK040(thi)051:412: dam tshig dang sdom pa bsrung snyam pa'i mos pa gyis /
NK040(thi)051:413: 'di ni khyod kyi dam tshig chu //
NK040(thi)051:414: dam tshig 'das nas bsreg par byed //
NK040(thi)051:415: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK040(thi)051:417: badz+ra pany+tsa a mri ta u tra ka th+aa th+aa /
NK040(thi)051:418: bcu pa bla ma'i bka' nyan pa'i sgo nas /
NK040(thi)051:420: bla mas ci ltar gsungs pa bzhin du bka' dang
NK040(thi)051:421: dam tshig la mi 'da' snyam pa'i mos pa gyis
NK040(thi)051:422: / rdo rje spyi bor bzhag la /
NK040(thi)051:423: dus 'di nyid la khyod nyid kyis //
NK040(thi)051:424: mkha' 'gro sde lnga nga yin gyis //
NK040(thi)051:425: nga yi ci ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK040(thi)051:426: khyod kyis skyo ba med par gyis //
NK040(thi)051:427: gang yang nga la brnyas pa min //
NK040(thi)051:428: de bzhin mos pa ma byas na //
NK040(thi)051:429: bdud kyis bcom nas dmyal bar 'gro //
NK040(thi)051:430: de bas dam tshig bus zung cig /
NK040(thi)051:432: bcu gcig pa dbang thob ma thob kyis skyon yon la gnyis te /
NK040(thi)051:433: dang po ma thob pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK040(thi)051:434: snod du mi rung bas gdams pa gcig nyan pa la mi dbang /
NK040(thi)051:435: skal ba med pas ngo sprod gdab tu mi rung /
NK040(thi)051:436: rjes gnang ba med pas nye du mi btub bo //
NK040(thi)051:438: dbang med pa la dngos grub med //
NK040(thi)051:439: bye ma btsir ba'i mar dang 'dra //
NK040(thi)051:440: de bas dbang bskur dam pa yin //
NK040(thi)051:441: bar du 'bad med blang bar byas //
NK040(thi)051:443: gnyis pa dbang thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK040(thi)051:444: gnas skabs su gdam pa zab mo nyan pa'i snod du rung bas /
NK040(thi)051:445: nam mkha' go 'byed kyis ngo sprad btab tu gtub /
NK040(thi)051:446: mthar thug sku lnga ye shes lnga /
NK040(thi)051:447: phrin las bzhi'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK040(thi)051:449: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK040(thi)051:450: sangs rgyas go 'phang rgyang mi ring //
NK040(thi)051:451: lag na rin chen thog pa'i mis //
NK040(thi)051:452: longs spyod rgyang mi ring ba bzhin //
NK040(thi)051:454: de yan chad sbyor ba'i dbang song /
NK040(thi)051:455: spyi don gnyis pa dngos bzhi'i rim pa la bzhi ste /
NK040(thi)051:461: dang po rdo rje mkha' 'gro bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK040(thi)051:462: man+dala 'bul zhing gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK040(thi)051:463: kye byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK040(thi)051:464: mchod cing ci ltar rtsal ba ltar //
NK040(thi)051:465: bdag kyang skyob pa'i don gyi phyir //
NK040(thi)051:466: rdo rje mkha' 'gro bum pa'i dbang //
NK040(thi)051:467: de ring bdag la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:469: de nas spros pa la dga' na /
NK040(thi)051:470: bkra shis kyi gleng bzhi dang /
NK040(thi)051:471: bkra shis dbang spyi dang mthun par brjod /
NK040(thi)051:473: pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma bzhi bsam /
NK040(thi)051:474: dbus kyi lte ba la ma cig lab kyi sgron ma /
NK040(thi)051:475: ngo bo bla ma dang dbyer med pa /
NK040(thi)051:476: rnam pa rdo rje rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma gcer
NK040(thi)051:477: bu mthing nag dur khrod kyi rgyan drug gsol ba
NK040(thi)051:479: thod pa'i dbu rgyan mdzad pa /
NK040(thi)051:480: phyag g.yas na thod pa bdud rtsi'i bkang ba bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)051:481: mchan khung na kha t+w+aam kha bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)051:482: gdan mi ro'i steng na bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)051:483: zhal cig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK040(thi)051:484: snyan cha rus pa'i rgyan 'ang mig bcug pa /
NK040(thi)051:485: zhabs g.yas bskum pa'i rting ba b+ha ga la gtad pa /
NK040(thi)051:487: sku la me ri dang me dpung 'bar ba gcig bsam /
NK040(thi)051:489: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro sku mdog dkar mo /
NK040(thi)051:490: rgyan cha lug gtso mo dang mthun par bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:491: lho yi pad 'dab la rin chen rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog ser mo /
NK040(thi)051:492: nub kyi pad 'dab la pad+ma rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK040(thi)051:493: byang gis pad 'dab la las kyi rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma ljang gu /
NK040(thi)051:495: cha lugs bzhugs tshul gtso mo ltar bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:496: de nas gtso mos ma pa bdud rtsi'i bkang pa phyag na bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)051:497: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)051:498: zhal nas 'di skad gsung par sgom /
NK040(thi)051:499: bla mas bum pa mgo thog tu bzung la /
NK040(thi)051:501: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya /
NK040(thi)051:502: sangs rgyas thugs ni rab bsgrub phyir /
NK040(thi)051:503: rdo rje mkha' 'gro khyed gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:504: badz+ra d+aak+ki ni a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK040(thi)051:507: ting nge 'dzin ni dbus kyi gtso mo'i brjod par bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:508: khyed rang rnams rdo rje mkha' 'gro mar gyur par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)051:509: steng gi nam mkha' la brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang /
NK040(thi)051:510: yi dam dpa' bo dpa' mo thams cad kyis bdud rtsi'i char phab /
NK040(thi)051:514: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis rlabs /
NK040(thi)051:515: mchog thun mong gis dngos grub thob par sgoms shig /
NK040(thi)051:517: ci ltar bltam pa tsam gyis ni //
NK040(thi)051:518: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK040(thi)051:519: lha yi chu ni dag pa yi //
NK040(thi)051:520: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK040(thi)051:521: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka te sa ma ya sh+ri ye h'u /
NK040(thi)051:522: dbang bskur bas dri ma dag /
NK040(thi)051:524: chu'i lhag ma yar spyi gtsug tu lud pa las /
NK040(thi)051:525: mi spyod pas dbu brgyan par bsgoms shig /
NK040(thi)051:527: ar+g+ham la sogs kyis mchod la /
NK040(thi)051:528: rol mo'i sgra thung ba cig bsgrags tshar ba'i rjes su bshad pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:530: rdo rje mkha' 'gro chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK040(thi)051:531: rnam par shes pa'i phung po rdo rje rigs kyi mkha' 'gro'i lha tshogs su dag /
NK040(thi)051:532: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang me long lta bu'i ye shes gnas par 'gyur /
NK040(thi)051:533: 'byung ba chu'i ngo bo lha mo ma ma ki'i sku thob pa'i bag chags dang /
NK040(thi)051:534: sa bon rgyud la bzhag pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:535: gnyis pa rin chen mkha' 'gro cod pan gyi dbang bskur la /
NK040(thi)051:536: dang po gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:537: kyee byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK040(thi)051:538: mchod cing ci ltar btsal ba ltar //
NK040(thi)051:539: bdag kyang skyob pa'i don gyis phyir //
NK040(thi)051:540: rin chen mkha' 'gro cod pan dbang //
NK040(thi)051:541: de ring khyod la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:543: de nas rin chen mkha' 'gro cod pan gyis dbang ni /
NK040(thi)051:544: lho phyogs kyi pad 'dab kyis steng na bzhugs pa'i
NK040(thi)051:545: rin chen mkha' 'gro'i rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan gyis khyed
NK040(thi)051:546: rang rnams kyis dbu la brgyan par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)051:547: zhal nas tshig 'di gsungs par bsgom zhig /
NK040(thi)051:548: rin chen mkha' 'gro dbu rgyan dbang //

NK040(thi)051:550: sangs rgyas yon tan rab bsgrub phyir //

NK040(thi)051:573: rin chen mkha' 'gro'i dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK040(thi)051:574: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen rigs kyi lha tshogs su dag /
NK040(thi)051:575: nyon mongs pa nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su gnas 'gyur /
NK040(thi)051:576: 'byung ba sa'i lha mo sangs rgyas spyan ma'i dbang
NK040(thi)051:577: thob cing bag chags dang sa bon rgyud la bzhag
NK040(thi)051:578: pa'o // gsum pa pad+ma mkha' 'gro'i dbang la /

NK040(thi)051:581: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la /
NK040(thi)051:582: mchod bdag kyang pad+ma mkha' 'gro rdo rje'i dbang //

NK040(thi)051:584: gser gyi rdo rje khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)051:585: zhal nas gsung bar bsgom zhig /
NK040(thi)051:587: de ring sangs rgyas gsung ni rab bsgrub phyir //

NK040(thi)051:592: khyed rang pad+ma mkha' 'gror gyur pa la //
NK040(thi)051:593: steng gis nam mkha' brgyud pa'i bla ma sogs 'agre'o //
NK040(thi)051:595: pad+ma mkha' 'gro'i rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas /
NK040(thi)051:596: 'du shes kyi phung po pad+ma rigs kyi lha tshogs su dag /
NK040(thi)051:597: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes gnas par 'gyur /
NK040(thi)051:598: 'byung ba me'i lha mo gos dkar mo'i dbang thob /
NK040(thi)051:599: bag chags dang sa bon rgyud la bzhag pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:600: bzhi pa las kyi mkha' 'gro'i dril bu'i dbang ste /
NK040(thi)051:601: dang po gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:603: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK040(thi)051:604: mchod bdag las kyi mkha' 'gro'i dril bu'i dbang //
NK040(thi)051:605: de ring khyod la ces brjod /
NK040(thi)051:607: byang gi pad 'dab steng na bzhugs pa'i las kyi
NK040(thi)051:608: mkha' 'gro'i dngul gyi dril bu khyod rnams kyi spyi
NK040(thi)051:610: zhal nas gsung tshig gsung pa'i bsgom cig /
NK040(thi)051:611: las kyi mkha' 'gro dril bu'i dbang /
NK040(thi)051:612: de ring khyod sangs rgyas phrin las rab bsgrub phyir /
NK040(thi)051:613: las kyi mkha' 'gro khyod gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:614: karma d+aak+ki ni a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK040(thi)051:615: tshig don slob dpon brjod kyang /
NK040(thi)051:616: las kyi mkha' 'gros brjod par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:617: khyed rang rnams las kyi mkha' 'gro mar gyur par bsgom la /

NK040(thi)051:622: nyon mongs pa phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su dag par gyur /
NK040(thi)051:623: 'byung ba rlung gis lha mo dam tshig sgrol ma'i dbang thob cing /
NK040(thi)051:624: bag chags dang sa bon rgyud la bzhag pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:625: lnga pa sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro ming gi dbang la dang po /
NK040(thi)051:628: byang chub rdo rje mchod bdag kyang sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro ming gis dbang //
NK040(thi)051:629: de ring khyod la ces brjod /

NK040(thi)051:635: sangs rgyas sku ni rab bsgrub phyir //
NK040(thi)051:636: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro khyod gyur cig /

NK040(thi)051:640: tshig slob dpon gyis brjod kyang /
NK040(thi)051:641: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gros brjod par bsam la /

NK040(thi)051:645: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro ming gi dbang bskur bas /

NK040(thi)051:647: nyon mongs pa gti mug chos kyi dbyings su ye shes su gnas gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:648: 'byung ba lha mo nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'i dbang thob cing /
NK040(thi)051:649: bag chags dang sa bon rgyud la bzhag pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:650: de rnams kyi ma rig pa rigs lngar bsgyur bas rig pa'i dbang lnga'o //
NK040(thi)051:651: drug pa gtso mo'i bdag po'i dbang ni /
NK040(thi)051:653: gsol ba 'debs pa'i rjes zlos mdzod cig /
NK040(thi)051:654: bla ma'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)051:655: gtso mo bdag gis dbang mchog 'di //
NK040(thi)051:656: bdag cag rnams la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:658: 'o mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i thang sku dang /
NK040(thi)051:660: me long rnams bla mas spyi bor bzhag par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)051:662: sangs rgyas kun gyi byin rlabs pas /
NK040(thi)051:663: rdo rje mkha' 'gro sku gsung thugs /
NK040(thi)051:664: blo chen khyod kyis bzung bar gyis /
NK040(thi)051:665: sangs rgyas rnams dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK040(thi)051:666: badz+ra d+aak+ki ni ka ya waka tsit+ta d+ha ra h'u /
NK040(thi)051:668: gtso mo'i bdag po'i dbang ni thob pa yin pas /
NK040(thi)051:669: gcod kyi skor nyan pa dang 'chang ba dang /
NK040(thi)051:670: nyams su len pa la dbang bar byed do //
NK040(thi)051:671: bdun pa rdo rje'i slob dpon gyi dbang ni /

NK040(thi)051:673: khyed zhabs pad+ma'i bka' drin gyis //
NK040(thi)051:674: bdag la rang dang gzhan gyi don //
NK040(thi)051:675: rdzogs phyir rdo rje slob dpon dbang //
NK040(thi)051:676: thugs rje'i gter phyes bdag la stsol //
NK040(thi)051:678: ngas khyed rang gis g.yas rdo rje gtad /
NK040(thi)051:681: mchan du kha t+w+aam gtad par bsgom zhig /
NK040(thi)051:683: rdo rje mkha' 'gro legs byin pa'i //
NK040(thi)051:684: rdo rje slob dpon dbang bskur ste /
NK040(thi)051:685: rdo rje 'dzin pa khyed gyur to //
NK040(thi)051:686: slob ma yongs su sdud par gyis //
NK040(thi)051:687: badz+ra d+aak+ki ni ma h+aa g+hu ru h'u /
NK040(thi)051:688: dag pa ni slob ma'i tshogs sdud nas gzhan don la dbang ba yin no //
NK040(thi)051:689: de bdun gyis bum dbang song /
NK040(thi)051:690: gnyis pa gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:692: gsol ba 'debs pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod cig /
NK040(thi)051:693: bla ma dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)051:694: gsang ba'i dbang mchog rin po che //
NK040(thi)051:695: bdag cag rnams la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:696: lan gnyis pa dang gsum pa'i rjes zlos mdzod cig /
NK040(thi)051:699: dbus kyi gtso mo rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma la thim /
NK040(thi)051:700: kha t+w+aam ga yab du gyur nas yab yum gnyis snyom par zhugs pas /
NK040(thi)051:701: thig le dkar dmar gtso mo'i b+ha ga'i nang du bab ste /
NK040(thi)051:702: tshur 'phros pas khyed rang rnams kyi lce thog tu byung bar bsgom zhig /
NK040(thi)051:704: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs //
NK040(thi)051:705: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pas //
NK040(thi)051:706: gsang ba'i gnas la legs byung bas //
NK040(thi)051:707: rigs kyi bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK040(thi)051:708: shu tra rag tra a mri ta h'u /
NK040(thi)051:710: sangs rgyas thams cad thig le dkar dmar gyi rnam par zhu nas /
NK040(thi)051:711: rang gis mgrin par thim par bsam pa ni gsang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK040(thi)051:712: gsum pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni /
NK040(thi)051:714: gsol ba gdab pa'i rjes zlos mdzod cig /
NK040(thi)051:715: bla ma dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)051:716: shes rab ye shes dbang mchog ni //
NK040(thi)051:717: bdag cag rnams la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:718: lan gnyis pa dang gsum pa'i rjes zlos mdzod cig /
NK040(thi)051:719: rje btsun ma'i tsaka li gtad la /
NK040(thi)051:721: gtso mo pho brang gi dbus nas byon te /
NK040(thi)051:722: skyes pa rnams kyi don du rdo rje mkha' 'gror gyur /
NK040(thi)051:723: bud med rnams kyi don du badz+ra he ru kar gyur ste /
NK040(thi)051:724: rang rang la zhal sbyor bar sgoms shig /
NK040(thi)051:727: stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pas //
NK040(thi)051:728: bde chen thabs dang shes rab 'di //
NK040(thi)051:729: khyod kyis rtag tu brten gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:730: sangs rgyas rnams dang mnyam par gyur //
NK040(thi)051:731: badz+ra ma h+aa su ka shu dz+ny+aa na h'u /
NK040(thi)051:732: ces brjod pas snyom par zhugs pas /
NK040(thi)051:733: bde stong dbyer med pa'i nyams rgyud la skye bar bsgom pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:734: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang yin no //
NK040(thi)051:735: bzhi pa tshig dbang bskur ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:737: gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK040(thi)051:738: bla ma dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)051:739: bzhi pa tshig dbang rin po che //
NK040(thi)051:740: bdag cag rnams la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:741: lan gnyis pa dang gsum pa'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK040(thi)051:743: yum rdo rje rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma de rang la thim /
NK040(thi)051:744: dbang bskur mkhan po slob dpon kyang rang la thim /
NK040(thi)051:745: rten snod bcud thams cad rang bzhin 'ja' yal ba bzhin stong pa nyid du song /
NK040(thi)051:746: dbang bskur mkhan gyi slob dpon /
NK040(thi)051:747: len pa'i slob ma dbang rdzas dang thams cad 'khor gsum yongs su dag par bsgom cig byas la /
NK040(thi)051:750: sgyu ma chen po rang bzhin che //
NK040(thi)051:751: thams cad chos sku mnyam pa nyid //
NK040(thi)051:752: rigs kyi bu khyod dbang bskur ro //
NK040(thi)051:753: sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+ha wa shud+d+ho&a ho /
NK040(thi)051:755: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang rig
NK040(thi)051:756: sems kyi cho 'phrul dag pa gsum gyi ngo bo
NK040(thi)051:757: dbyer med stong pa rang bzhin yin snyam du bsam
NK040(thi)051:758: mo // de rnams ni dbang bzhi gdan thog gcig tu bsdus pa'i cho ga'o //
NK040(thi)051:760: spyi don gsum pa rjes la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)051:761: yum chen gyi gtor dbang dang /
NK040(thi)051:762: ma cig gi gtor dbang dang /
NK040(thi)051:766: bla ma dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)051:767: gtor ma'i dbang chog dam pa ni //
NK040(thi)051:768: bdag cag rnams la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:769: ces lan gsum dbang gtor slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK040(thi)051:771: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor gtor ma 'di dang
NK040(thi)051:772: tha dad med par chos sku yum chen mo la
NK040(thi)051:773: sras phyogs bcu sangs rgyas dang /
NK040(thi)051:774: bla ma brgyud pa dang bcas pas bskor nas bzhugs par bsgom la /
NK040(thi)051:775: brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs byed tshar nas /
NK040(thi)051:776: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i bla ma rnams kyis byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK040(thi)051:777: ma cig lab sgron mas byin gyis yum chen mo
NK040(thi)051:778: shes rab kyis pha rol tu phyin mas byin gyis
NK040(thi)051:779: da lta nyid du byin gyis rlobs shig /
NK040(thi)051:781: chos sku yum chen mo 'khor dang bcas pa 'od
NK040(thi)051:782: du zhu nas khyed rang rnams la thim par bsgom
NK040(thi)051:784: ma cig lab sgron gyi gtor dbang ni /
NK040(thi)051:785: dbang gtor la skyems mchod bya /
NK040(thi)051:786: man+dala 'bul la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:787: bla ma dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams //
NK040(thi)051:788: gtor ma'i dbang mchog dam pa 'di //
NK040(thi)051:789: bdag cag rnams la bskur du gsol //
NK040(thi)051:791: slob ma'i spyi bor gtor ma bzhag la /
NK040(thi)051:793: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bor gtor ma dang tha
NK040(thi)051:794: dad med par ma cig sku mdog dkar mo gzhung
NK040(thi)051:795: ltar bskyed la / de'i phyi rol shar rdo rje
NK040(thi)051:796: mkha' 'gro la rdo rje mkha' 'gro 'bum gyis bskor
NK040(thi)051:797: ltar bskyed la / ba / de bzhin du lho
NK040(thi)051:798: rin chen mkha' 'gro la nub pad+ma mkha' 'gro la
NK040(thi)051:799: pad+ma byang las kyi las kyi ces de dang /
NK040(thi)051:800: de'i phyi rol du sha za'i mkha' 'gro dang /
NK040(thi)051:801: 'jig rten mkha' 'gros sprin dpung gtib pa ltar bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:802: gsol 'debs lan mo byed du gzhug /
NK040(thi)051:803: yum chen thugs las sprul pa'i sras //
NK040(thi)051:806: de nas ma cig 'od du zhu nas gtor chu blud pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:807: dam pa'i gtor dbang byed pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:809: gtor ma mi dmigs pa las pad zla'i steng du
NK040(thi)051:810: dam pa rgya gar sku mdog smug nag seng ldeng
NK040(thi)051:812: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas d+aa ma ru dang g.yon
NK040(thi)051:813: pas mi rkang gis gling bu tshag tshag 'bud pa
NK040(thi)051:814: / spyan khra hrig hrig mdzad pa /
NK040(thi)051:815: de'i spyi bor bka' rgyud kyi bla ma bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)051:817: g.yon du mkha' 'gro mdun du dam can /
NK040(thi)051:819: skabs na d+aak+ki ma rnams kyis bskor bar dmigs la /
NK040(thi)051:820: slob mas gsol 'debs kyi lan mo byed cing /
NK040(thi)051:821: rje bla ma rnams la sogs dam pa'i rtag bstod byed cing /
NK040(thi)051:823: dam pa 'khor dang bcas pa 'od du zhu nas /
NK040(thi)051:824: khyed rang rnams la thim par bsgom //
NK040(thi)051:825: ces brjod la gtor chu blud /
NK040(thi)051:826: des rjes kyi bya ba song /
NK040(thi)051:827: de ltar sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi dbang bskur chos kyi go 'byed kun dga' 'bum pas bris pa'o ////
NK040(thi)051:828: gcod dbang nam mkha' go 'byed rgyas spros can bzhugs /
NK040(thi)051:830: bla ma dam pa'i zhabs la gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)051:831: rgyal ba'i yum gyur shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK040(thi)051:832: skye 'gag mtha' bral de la gus btud nas //
NK040(thi)051:833: 'gro la phan phyir skye med gcig chod kyis //
NK040(thi)051:834: chos dbang sems la bskur ba bri bar bya //
NK040(thi)051:835: de la shes rab kyis pha rol tu phyin pa skye med gcig chod du bstan pa /
NK040(thi)051:836: bka' brgyud don gyi man ngag /
NK040(thi)051:837: bka' dngos kyi sgo nas slob ma rjes su bzung ba la gsum ste /
NK040(thi)051:841: dang po la bcu gnyis ste /
NK040(thi)051:844: bgegs gtor btang zhing bzlas pa bya ba dang /
NK040(thi)051:845: dam tshig pa bskyed pa dang /
NK040(thi)051:846: ye shes sems dpa' spyan 'dren pa dang /
NK040(thi)051:850: mchod pa byin gyis rlabs cing 'bul ba /
NK040(thi)051:855: dang po man+dala dang mchod gtor bya ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:858: bas mtha' la sogs bla gab med par /
NK040(thi)051:860: bla re dang yol ba bres nas /
NK040(thi)051:861: sku gsung thugs kyis rten bkram /
NK040(thi)051:862: de la man+dala gru bzhi la ba yi rnam lngas byug /
NK040(thi)051:863: thig gdab pad+ma 'dab bcu phyogs mtshon bya /
NK040(thi)051:864: lte ba ser po gru chad ljang ku khyams phyogs mtshon bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:865: de nas pad+ma'i lte ba dang 'dab ma la /
NK040(thi)051:866: me tog tshom bu bcu gcig bkod /
NK040(thi)051:868: gru chad la bzhi ste bcu dgu bkod /
NK040(thi)051:869: lha bshos dang gtor ma lha grangs dang mnyam par bkod /
NK040(thi)051:870: gtor ma bzang po gcig la /
NK040(thi)051:871: sha dang khur ba la sogs pa'i tshogs rdzas dang /
NK040(thi)051:872: rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa pad+ma'i lte bar steg gi steng du bzhag go //
NK040(thi)051:873: de la mchod pa 'byor tshad kyis bskor bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:874: gnyis pa bgegs gtor btang zhing bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:875: slob ma du yod pa'i grangs dang mnyam pa'i glud gtor byas la /
NK040(thi)051:876: lan chags kyis mgron la sbyin la bka' bsgo bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:877: slob ma rnams kyis brgyad stong ngam /
NK040(thi)051:879: yum gyis bskyed rims bstan nas ga te bzlas su bzhugs la chu gtor btang /
NK040(thi)051:880: des ni dpon slob rnams la bar chad mi 'ong ba yin no //
NK040(thi)051:882: gsum pa dam tshig pa bskyed pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:884: rin chen sna bzhi las grub pa'i pho brang gis dbus su /
NK040(thi)051:885: pad+ma'i sdong po chen po yal ga lo 'dab rgyas pa /
NK040(thi)051:886: nam mkha' thams cad khengs par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:887: de'i dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma bcu'i lte ba la /
NK040(thi)051:888: seng+ge dang pad zla'i steng du yum chen mo shes rab kyis pha rol tu phyin ma /
NK040(thi)051:889: sku mdog gser gtso ma lta bu zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK040(thi)051:890: zhabs rdo rje'i dkyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK040(thi)051:891: g.yas dang po rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK040(thi)051:892: 'og ma shes rab kyi ral gri /
NK040(thi)051:894: 'og ma na shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i po ti bsnams pa /
NK040(thi)051:895: lang tsho dar la bab pa rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK040(thi)051:897: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi brjid can du bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:898: de'i g.yas su mar me mdzad la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams bsam /
NK040(thi)051:899: g.yon du byams pa la sogs pa'i ma byon pa'i sangs rgyas rnams bsam /
NK040(thi)051:900: steng gi nam mkhar sh+aakya thub pa la sogs da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dang /
NK040(thi)051:901: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams dang yi dam mabazhugasa par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:902: de nas shar phyogs kyis 'dab ma la thugs las
NK040(thi)051:903: 'khrungs pa'i sras yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK040(thi)051:904: dkon mchog 'byung gnas bzhugs par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:905: de bzhin du lhor mya ngan med pa'i dpal /
NK040(thi)051:907: byang du rgyal ba'i dbang po /
NK040(thi)051:908: byang shar du ting nge 'dzin gyi glang po dam pa'i dpal /
NK040(thi)051:909: lho nub tu nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor snang ba dam pa'i dpal /
NK040(thi)051:910: nub byang du gdug dam pa'i dpal /
NK040(thi)051:911: yang shar gyi 'dab ma la dga' ba'i dpal /
NK040(thi)051:912: nub kyis 'dab ma la pad+ma'i dpal bzhugs par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:913: de dag kyang chos 'chad kyi phyag rgya can /
NK040(thi)051:914: sprul sku'i cha lugs sku mdog ma nges so //
NK040(thi)051:915: rang rang gis 'khor gyis bskor bar bsam /
NK040(thi)051:916: pad+ma'i yal ga phra mo rnams gyes pa la /
NK040(thi)051:917: lha'i bu dang bu mo rnams kyi me tog gi char 'bebs pa /
NK040(thi)051:921: glu'i mchod pa 'bul ba la sogs pa dpag tu med par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:923: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK040(thi)051:924: kun dga' bo la sogs nyan thos dpag tu med pa rnams kyang bzhugs par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:929: dri za la sogs pa rnams yum la 'dud pa'i tshul du bsam /
NK040(thi)051:930: gru chad la mchod pa'i lha mo rnams bsam /
NK040(thi)051:932: shar du 'phags skyes po dkar po /
NK040(thi)051:934: nub tu spyan mi bzang dmar po /
NK040(thi)051:935: byang du rnam thos sras ljang gu /
NK040(thi)051:936: de rnams kyang rang rang gis 'khor dpag tu med pas bskor nas /
NK040(thi)051:937: mchod pa dpag tu med pa 'bul nas bstan pa bsrung bar bsam /
NK040(thi)051:938: de ltar gnas de nyid gnas 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du blta bar bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:939: bzhi pa ye shes pa spyan drang ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:940: rang gis snying kha nas 'od 'phros pas /
NK040(thi)051:941: yum chen mo 'khor dang bcas pa spyan 'dren par bya ste /
NK040(thi)051:942: ma lus sems can kun gyis mgon gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:943: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'jom mdzad lha //
NK040(thi)051:944: dngos rnams ma lus ci bzhin mkhyen gyur pas //
NK040(thi)051:945: yum chen 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:946: thugs las skyes pa'i phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK040(thi)051:947: byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos tshogs rnams dang //
NK040(thi)051:948: tshangs pa brgya byin rgyal po chen po bzhi //
NK040(thi)051:949: bstan pa srung mdzad 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:950: e h+ya hi b+ha g+ha wan ma h+aa ka ru
NK040(thi)051:951: ni ka tri sha sa pa ri wa ra sa
NK040(thi)051:952: ma ya s+t+wam / badz+ra sa ma ya dza dzah ces pas spyan 'dren la /
NK040(thi)051:954: lnga pa mchod yon 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:955: yum chen 'dir ni byon pa legs //
NK040(thi)051:956: bdag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK040(thi)051:957: bdag gis mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK040(thi)051:958: 'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:959: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta ga ga na pu tsa me ga sa ma ye h'u /
NK040(thi)051:960: ces pas lha mo mchod yon thog pa mang pos 'bul /
NK040(thi)051:961: drug pa sku khrus gsol ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:962: ci ltar bltam pa tsam gyis ni //
NK040(thi)051:963: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK040(thi)051:964: lha'i chu ni dag pa yi //
NK040(thi)051:965: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK040(thi)051:966: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi pra b+hi sad ka ra pra ti dza h'u /
NK040(thi)051:967: zhes lha mos bum chu thog pas khrus gsol /
NK040(thi)051:970: yum chen bdag la brtse dgongs ste //
NK040(thi)051:971: ci srid mchod pa bdag bgyis pa //
NK040(thi)051:972: de srid yum chen bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:973: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma ka ma la ye s+t+wam /
NK040(thi)051:974: ces phun sum tshogs pa'i gdan 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)051:975: brgyad pa mchod pa sbyin pa byed cing 'bul ba ni /
NK040(thi)051:976: ga te'i sngags lan bdun brjod pas /
NK040(thi)051:977: mchod rdzas kyi nyes skyon dang dri ma dag nas gtsang bar byas par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:980: mchod pa rnams lngas 'dod yon lnga dang rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun dang /
NK040(thi)051:981: mchod pa'i sprin bsam gyis mi khyab par bsam /
NK040(thi)051:982: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK040(thi)051:983: mchod yon ci snyed yod pa dang //
NK040(thi)051:985: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhugs su gsol //
NK040(thi)051:986: na ma sarba ta tha ga ta ar+g+ham pra ti
NK040(thi)051:987: tsa pu dza me g+ha sa mu tra s+pha ra
NK040(thi)051:989: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK040(thi)051:990: me tog ji snyed yum chen thugs rje push+pe sogs de bzhin du /
NK040(thi)051:992: d+hu pe snang gsal a lo ke dri mchog g+han+d+he
NK040(thi)051:993: zhal zas ne we d+ye sgra snyan shap+da sogs sbyar
NK040(thi)051:994: la spros pa la dga' na /
NK040(thi)051:995: 'dod yon lnga rat+na la sogs pa mchod par bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:996: yum gtor ni sngar gtor ma gzhan dang dus gcig /
NK040(thi)051:998: ga te'i sngags sham du kha hi ces 'bul lo //
NK040(thi)051:1000: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK040(thi)051:1001: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK040(thi)051:1002: dkon mchog gsum gyi rtsa ba ste //
NK040(thi)051:1003: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK040(thi)051:1004: bla ma'i sku ni rdo rje'i sku //
NK040(thi)051:1005: mdzes shing lta bas chog mi shes //
NK040(thi)051:1006: bsam gyi mi khyab yon tan ldan //
NK040(thi)051:1007: bla ma'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1008: bla ma'i gsung ni tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK040(thi)051:1009: bdag med seng+ge'i sgra sgrogs shing //
NK040(thi)051:1010: mu steg log lta 'joms mdzad pa'i //
NK040(thi)051:1011: bla ma'i gsungs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1012: bla ma'i thugs ni nam mkha' 'dra //
NK040(thi)051:1013: bde gsal mi rtog ngang tshul can //
NK040(thi)051:1014: rnam thar gsum la nges 'byung ba'i //
NK040(thi)051:1015: bla ma'i thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1016: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK040(thi)051:1017: ma skyes mi 'gags nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK040(thi)051:1018: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK040(thi)051:1019: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1020: blta bas mi ngom 'gro ba'i dpal du shar //
NK040(thi)051:1021: zhal gcig phyag bzhi gtso ma gser gyi mdog /
NK040(thi)051:1022: rin chen rgyan spras rdo rje'i dkyil krung bzhugs //
NK040(thi)051:1023: rgyal ba'i yum gyur khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1024: zhing khams rnam dag gser gyi sa gzhi la //
NK040(thi)051:1025: rin chen rnam pa mang po gcal du bkram //
NK040(thi)051:1026: me tog pun+da ri ka char du 'beb //
NK040(thi)051:1027: yum gyur dge ma khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1028: tshogs gnyis las 'khrungs yid bzhin dpag bsam shing //
NK040(thi)051:1029: 'gro ba'i re skong gang la gang 'dul gyis //
NK040(thi)051:1030: sems can ma lus smin cing grol mdzad pa'i //
NK040(thi)051:1031: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1032: stong nyid bco brgyad chos kyi sdong po la //
NK040(thi)051:1033: tshad med bzhi'i lo 'dab rgyas gyur cig /
NK040(thi)051:1034: skye 'gags med pa'i 'bras bu so sor smin //
NK040(thi)051:1035: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK040(thi)051:1036: de nas tshogs mchod dang grib chog bya /
NK040(thi)051:1037: bcu pa slob ma'i blo bcos pa ni /
NK040(thi)051:1039: 'chi ba mi rtag pa las rgyu 'bras 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs rnams bshad par bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:1040: bcu gcig pa skyabs 'gro sems bskyed ni /
NK040(thi)051:1042: chos stong nyid snying rje dbyer med pa /
NK040(thi)051:1043: dge 'dun dag pa'i sa la gnas pa la skyabs su 'gro ste /
NK040(thi)051:1044: rang gi lus longs spyod thams cad mchod par 'bul la /
NK040(thi)051:1045: bla ma la sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes bzhag la /
NK040(thi)051:1048: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK040(thi)051:1049: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK040(thi)051:1050: rkang gnyis dam pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK040(thi)051:1051: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK040(thi)051:1052: zhi ba 'dod chags bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK040(thi)051:1053: don dam pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK040(thi)051:1055: sa chen po la rab tu gnas pa'i byang chub
NK040(thi)051:1056: sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po phyir mi ldog pa'i
NK040(thi)051:1057: dge 'dun pa rnams la skyabs mchi'o //

NK040(thi)051:1412: dag bya ngag gis sgrib pa dag /
NK040(thi)051:1414: de'i ngang la gsal stong 'dzin med bsgom /
NK040(thi)051:1415: de bas bsdus pa byed na ma cig bzhi ka dkar po byed gsungs /
NK040(thi)051:1416: ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur dang /
NK040(thi)051:1417: tshogs byin gyis rlabs cing rol pa dang /
NK040(thi)051:1418: rjes kyi cho ga rnams gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK040(thi)051:1419: thun mong ma yin pa'i bka' dbang 'di gsang bar bya'o //
